<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">这个时代有好多海中生物的化石。<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我们常说<delay8 />大海是我们的母亲，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />生命的源头果然还是大海呀。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">古代的生物们<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总是有着奇怪的姿态呀。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家应该都是为它们这种<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起来有一点点吓人，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但又感觉可爱的造型而吸引的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />眼前的这些，<delay20 />
都是生物们最初的姿态<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />究竟是经过了<delay8 />多少次的进化，<delay20 />
它们才成为如今的样子呢？<10_4 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />让人感受到一种久远的浪漫！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大大的化石<delay20 />
看起来非常壮观，我个人很喜欢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />踏进展览室的时候，我一个大人<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也抑制不住那种激动的心情呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像恐龙这种<delay8 />巨大的生物，<delay20 />
即便如今站在化石前，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我还是难以相信它们真实存在过。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这种<delay8 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大就是强<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />的感觉<delay20 />
非常有古代生物的风格，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以说是相当直观了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然化石只是骨骼的造型，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但却是魄力十足<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果紧盯着它们看<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就会感觉<delay20 />随时都可能突然动起来，<delay8 />
稍微有那么一点恐怖<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">回顾地球的历史，<delay8 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />生物都已经历过<delay8 />
许多次濒临灭绝的危机了。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然而只要地球<delay8 />依然存在，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我相信还会有<delay8 />其他种类的生物<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />将生命延续下去的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />化石都是从古老的地层中<delay8 />
被发掘的对不对？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />古老的地面层层叠叠不断反复，<delay20 />
可是<delay8 />地球也并没有因此而变大<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是不可思议呀。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是还有许多未知生物的化石<delay20 />
没被发掘出来呢？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />远古世界实在是太浪漫了……<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="100_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你比较喜欢哪一块化石？<delay20 />
不用急，<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />尽情地看吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你觉得<tag a="110" b="32" />上的<colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />怎么样？<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这里对化石的展览方式<delay20 />
应该<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还挺不错的吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">独自看着这些化石，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />突然就感觉有些寂寞<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有你在真是太好了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="200_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />博物馆<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />也算是彰显小<tag a="110" b="32" />地位的一环，<delay8 />
你也是这么想的吧？<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我一直等着它开张呢。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是待在这个庄严肃穆的空间里，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就感到<delay8 />自己的水准
仿佛有所提升了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我今天来看看化石展览室。<delay20 />
这个房间使用的展示方法，<delay8 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉特别能<delay8 />激发想象力呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />自己居住的<tag a="110" b="32" />上能建成<colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" />，<delay8 />
真的是一件大好事呀！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在刚落成的<colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" />里<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />发觉了不少有趣之处，真开心呀。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来，这间房间的照明效果明显，<delay20 />
感觉<anim id="Sleepy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有些昏昏沉沉<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>